<body>
  {{>nav}}
  <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid mt-4" style="margin-bottom:0rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-1">&lt;Hello, world!&gt;</h1>
      <p class="display-4 mt-4">I am a full-stack developer <br /> based in Raleigh, NC.</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      <h2>Let me help you build your next project!</h2>
      <a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#contactModal">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid bg-dark text-light">
    <div class="container p-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <a name="about" class="anchor">
            <h1 class="text-center display-4 pt-4 pb-4 mt-4 mb-4">
              "I don't know. Brent can figure it out."
            </h1>
          </a>
          <p class="pb-4 mb-4">
            That phrase has been responsible for an enormous variety of opportunities and experiences, and now I've made a career out of being the guy people call when they have a problem they don't know how to solve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid bg-secondary">
    <div class="container p-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg">
          <a name="projects" class="anchor">
            <h1 class="text-center text-light display-4 pb-4 mb-4">
              Projects
            </h1>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-dark">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Dungeons &amp; Dragons 5e Character Builder</h5>
              <p class="card-text">A tool I put together for some friends to help them build new characters for their D&amp;D games</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">View this Project</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">California RCFE Finder</h5>
              <p class="card-text">A tool I put together to help visualize RCFE density in the state of California.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">View this Project</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Carefield Living</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Company website for Carefield Living, a brand of senior assisted living and memory care communities.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">View this Project</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">MotoQuest</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Company website for MotoQuest, an adventure motorcycle tour operator.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">Go somewhere</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Card title</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">Go somewhere</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x200" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Card title</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">Go somewhere</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid bg-info">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-info p-4" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#contactModal">
      Contact Me
    </button>
  </div>
  <!--modal content-->
  <div class="modal fade" id="contactModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="contactModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="contactModalLabel">Contact Me</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>
            Let me know how I can help you!
          </p>
          <form>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="inputEmail">Email address</label>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" id="inputEmail" aria-describedby="emailHelp">
              <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">I'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="inputMessage">Message</label>
              <textarea type="" class="form-control" id="inputMessage" rows="3"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Send</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--scripts-->
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
